WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:03.900
&gt;&gt; Zac Gordon: One of the biggest things
that's come out lately is a product called

2
00:00:03.900 --> 00:00:05.150
Calypso.

3
00:00:05.150 --> 00:00:09.850
And so Calypso is built on React,
it's completely a single

4
00:00:09.850 --> 00:00:14.280
page web app design and not only does it
rebuild the entire admin area of WordPress

5
00:00:14.280 --> 00:00:19.470
in JavaScript in React, but it also has
other abilities like checking stats.

6
00:00:19.470 --> 00:00:22.850
Letting you manage multiple
blogs all in one place.

7
00:00:22.850 --> 00:00:27.650
Letting you track and read other
people's blogs all from one admin area.

8
00:00:27.650 --> 00:00:31.130
And so Calypso was put out
by the folks at Automatic.

9
00:00:31.130 --> 00:00:33.440
And this is where if you're not
as familiar with WordPress,

10
00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:35.370
it's important to make a distinction.

11
