There's something called WordPress.org,
which is the open source version of

12
00:00:39.205 --> 00:00:42.090
WordPress that we're working with
today and that you could download and

13
00:00:42.090 --> 00:00:43.810
run in your site or run locally.

14
00:00:43.810 --> 00:00:48.180
