work full time on WordPress, but

17
00:00:57.170 --> 00:00:58.160
also on Calypso.

18
00:00:58.160 --> 00:01:02.570
So now there are people who's jobs
are just to support the software.

19
00:01:02.570 --> 00:01:07.160
Now, you can not easily just take
Calypso as this new admin interface and

20
00:01:07.160 --> 00:01:11.970
run it in a .org installation it's
really set up for the .com environment.

21
00:01:11.970 --> 00:01:14.880
